=== Festivals ===
Rites are held on {{ill|lt=January 15|Q2260|WD=Q2260|1=January 15}} and {{ill|lt=October 15|Q2919|WD=Q2919|1=October 15}}{{Sfn|Mishima City History Vol. 2|1988|p=561}}; the latter is the annual festival<ref name="board">Explanatory board in the precincts.</ref>.

